/* eslint-disable jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid */ import React from "react"; const ConfirmModal = ({ title, innerHtml, textOk, textCancel, onOk, onCancel, }) => { return (
{title}
{innerHtml}
onOk()} className="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" data-dismiss="modal" > {textOk}
onCancel()} className="btn btn-third btn-lg btn-block" data-dismiss="modal" > {textCancel}
); }; export default ConfirmModal;
